desc_short	-----								Kingdoms CCG is an exciting, feature-rich trading card game featuring 27 unique heroes, over 900 cards, guilds, crafting and tournaments with prizes! Find your Kingdom and join the battle for control of the fantasy world of Euna. Victory awaits!							
